"\"<tt>fakeroot debian/rules binary-indep</tt>\" runs \"<tt>fakeroot dh "
"binary-indep</tt>\"; which in turn runs almost the same sequence as "
"\"<tt>fakeroot dh binary</tt>\" but excluding <prgn>dh_strip</prgn>, "
